{"tid":513285,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"豎中指都唔得？印度律師起訴 WhatsApp 粗鄙犯法","createTime":"2017-12-29T10:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T13:29:13.000Z","uid":66607,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"51060f2b3367437a6a7bbcdcaa4c01839ddce32d","tid":513285,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"就算 Emoji 表情符號的設計可愛，但用嚟鬧人始終會讓人感覺冒犯。最近一名印度律師 Gurmeet Singh 就向即時通訊軟件 WhatsApp 發出警告，表示軟件內含有粗鄙的「豎中指」Emoji，違反了當地有關淫穢、猥褻和無禮手勢的法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSingh 引用印度刑法第 354 和 509 節，指向女士展示淫穢、猥褻或無禮的手勢，或任何人使用淫穢、猥褻、無禮的手勢均屬違法；他又指愛爾蘭的法律同樣認為對他人豎起中指屬於違法。Singh 表示 WhatsApp 提供「豎中指」Emoji，就等於直接教唆使用淫穢、猥褻、無禮的手勢。如果 WhatsApp 無法在 15 天內將「豎中指」Emoji 刪除，他就會從民事或刑事方式入稟控告 WhatsApp。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp 暫時未就此事作出官方回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/209800/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F209800%2F1%2F&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9gHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=5bbae34d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/209800/1/</a>"},{"pid":"524707079e80766f1d1ce4b68508013e84df5c0d","tid":513285,"uid":119349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"🖕"},{"pid":"fad25ccbf17648aa2c6e9e148df97d1b1b37c5b5","tid":513285,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"🤙"},{"pid":"7d4b8841b14fb7de33f8adbe929aca1ecfc319c7","tid":513285,"uid":36702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"朋友，番.... .jpg"},{"pid":"15a985b21a6ad4354550c496e20c9cf1a4660782","tid":513285,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafbecb820e922aad135820f4b37ccfb932